MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

2004-2107. Disciplinary Counsel v. Goetz.

It is ordered by this court, sua sponte, that William G. Goetz is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of November 16, 2005, to wit: Failure to pay the civil penalty in the amount of $30,000.00 on or before December 16, 2005.
